   PLAYLIST MANAGER (Userscript) — unified styling
   Expected containers/classes (stable in our master):
   #erika-playlist-panel (root, docked)
   .erika-toolbar       (top control bar)
   .erika-search        (search input area)
   .erika-grid          (card grid/list)
   .erika-item          (single playlist/item row)
   .erika-collapsible   (section wrapper w/ data-state)
   .erika-dropzone      (import/export/drag target)
   ========================================================= */

